parameters:
\N<Arashi>Ahh, I'm seriously beat... Luna-chan, let's take a little
break, yeah?♪

\N<Luna>Yes, I'm quite tired too... Ah, I wish I had brought
something to drink.
\N<Arashi>Oh, perfect timing! I've got something good with me～♪

\N<Arashi>Ta-da! A potion that blows away fatigue when you drink it～
This one's for you, Luna-chan♪

\N<Luna>Eh!?... Is that okay? Don't you only have enough for
yourself, Arashi-san...

\N<Arashi>It's fine, it's fine～ Don't hold back♪ Just being with Luna-
chan is healing enough for me♪
Will you drink the potion offered by Arashi?

\N<Luna>If Arashi-san says it's okay, then I'll gratefully accept
it♪
\N<Arashi>Okay♪ Go on, chug it down～ chug♪
\N<Luna>Here goes♪ Glug, glug... Phew! Wow, this is delicious!
\N<Arashi>Yeah yeah, everyone who drinks it says that～♪

\N<Luna>Is that so? It's delicious and... somehow, my body feels
light and floaty...
\N<Luna>Huh... Why am I... suddenly so sleepy～...

\N<Arashi>You must be really tired～♪ It's okay, go ahead and sleep～
I'll keep watch over you♪

\N<Arashi>...Alright, perfect, just the two of us in the cabin...♪ Now
then, time to "heal my fatigue" with Luna-chan's body～
A reminiscence scene has been added
Impression of Arashi has been updated
"1_t=9_subject=男の人の前で寝ちゃった…大丈夫、だったよね..."
"1_t=5_subject=彼を支えて、早く元の…幸せな生活を過ごしたい"
"1_t=6_subject=一緒にいるだけで安心する人なんて他にいない"
1 new notification: There is a new post on SNS

\N<Luna>No... I feel bad about it, so please, Arashi-san, you drink
it
\N<Arashi>Ah, really?... I'm fine without it, so I'll pass for now

\N<Arashi>It's totally fine～♪ But if you ever want some, just let me
know? I'll let you drink anytime♪

Arashi put away the potion with a somewhat disappointed look
on his face
\N<Bob>Oh! What a nice resting spot we've found♪

\N<Luna>You've done well to come this far, Bob-san. We've reached
quite a deep place, so let's take a proper break.

\N<Bob>Okay! I agree!... By the way, Luna, you seem pretty tired,
huh?
\N<Luna>Well, yes... But I'll be fine after a little rest.
\N<Bob>Then let me take care of that fatigue for you!
\N<Luna>Eh, Bob-san, can you use healing magic?
\N<Bob>No no! Not magic, I'll soothe you with these hands of mine♪

\N<Bob>Actually, I learned how to massage from a friend of mine!
With these hands, I'll say goodbye to your fatigue.

\N<Luna>Wow, that's amazing you can do massages! What should I do...
(It means being touched by a man...)
\N<Luna>Then, since you're offering, please go ahead♪
\N<Bob>Okay❤ I'll relax you with my hands♪

\N<Bob>But still... I'm worried if I can do it properly since even
my hands can't fully grasp the size♪
A reminiscence scene has been added.
Impression of Bob has been updated.
"1_t=8_subject=マッサージもできるんだ…でも胸って普通なの!?"
"1_t=5_subject=彼を支えて、早く元の…幸せな生活を過ごしたい"
"1_t=6_subject=一緒にいるだけで安心する人なんて他にいない"
1 new notification: There is a new post on SNS.
\N<Luna>No, actually, I'm fine. You should rest as well, Bob-san.
\N<Bob>I'm full of energy! This super body doesn't get tired!
\N<Luna>Your concern is enough, thank you♪ Let's rest well?

\N<Bob>Mmm- okay then... If you ever need a massage, just let me
know...
\N<Luna>Yes, I will ask you when the time comes♪

Bob tried to close the distance with Luna but it seems it
didn't go as planned...

It doesn't seem like monsters will invade here, shall we
take a short break?
